It’s understood he was coming back from the conference when he was shot in Umlazi. DURBAN – African National Congress (ANC) in KwaZulu-Natal Youth League secretary Thanduxolo Sabela has confirmed that chairperson of the ANC Youth League at the Coastal College campus in Umlazi, Bongani Usher Mkhize, has been shot dead. It’s understood he was coming back from the conference when he was shot in Umlazi.    More to follow.